"n.床垫 【考】 tablecloth : table / sheet : mattress(桌布用来铺桌子/床 单用来铺床) 【记】 分割记忆：mat(席子 ，草席)+tress(头发) 【例】 I have back problems, so I sleep on a very firm mattress. n. (长方形的)床垫 【记】源于: mat(n 席子) 【类】tablecloth: table = sheet: mattress桌布用来铺桌子 = 床单用来铺床 【记】mat 席子 + tress 一绺头发, 枝条 mattress (n.)  late 13c., from Old French materas (12c., Modern French matelas), from Italian materasso and directly from Medieval Latin matracium, borrowed in Sicily from Arabic al-matrah ""the cushion"" (also source of Spanish almadraque ""mattress,"" Provençal almatrac), literally ""the thing thrown down,"" from taraha ""he threw (down)."""
